page.title: 20Local news 4thJuly 1985
page.content: Mrs.Hodkin said there were about 18 cows coming towrds them.She told the children not to worry as they were just curious about the dog.Then the cows pushed the lady over and the lady got up again but the cows pushed her over again and started trampling on her. {House for sale.}Urchfont.A delightfully modernised detached period cottage quietly tucked away in a No Through Road.Sitting room 19ft by 13ft.Dining room,fitted kitchen.3/4bedrooms including galleried bedroom.Bathroom.Gardens in all approx. threequarters of an acre.Offers in excess of Â£60,000.
